{"tid":461373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"贈送腦魔bb","createTime":"2017-11-07T13:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T17:02:28.000Z","uid":3098,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0be1a5a0f6d0af13a927b637c86b69f2aeb8be42","tid":461373,"uid":3098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:47:36.000Z","msg":"話說之前買左兩隻腦魔bb <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/214417_4f5c8ae23e2fd26f16f21ca1aaf7924a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F214417_4f5c8ae23e2fd26f16f21ca1aaf7924a.jpg&h=0c32aa9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係間房裝修完就無位擺佢地 希望有巴絲可以收留佢地<br />\n兩隻都無攬過 一直都只係放係架上面<br />\n原價好似160/2隻 <br />\n有心既可以請我食餐飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔請都無所謂<br />\n只係希望你可以好好對佢地 <br />\n有興趣既可以tg我 <a href=\"https://t.me/acupofmocha\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Facupofmocha&d=dM30yAcC%2B%2F4wfHYmLqsYTLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=46304ad5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/acupofmocha</a>"},{"pid":"57b7694e23cb975548bc448d050a416a06583262","tid":461373,"uid":84934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T15:37:13.000Z","msg":"仲有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0126f04d3dd7c3c0671ec4d808b6c13979198135","tid":461373,"uid":129453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"仲有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />綠色個隻好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae13d60ca636a66d982f2110a1d19971c309f8b6","tid":461373,"uid":157551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T15:47:37.000Z","msg":"仲有無? 真心想要"},{"pid":"aa0d3a1680ec36429a086fbde8825c56f4c94275","tid":461373,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"reply